1 Section 1. Section 83-4,114.02, Reissue Revised Statutes of
2 Nebraska, is amended to read:
3 83-4,114.02 (1) Before disciplinary measures are taken against an
4 inmate for drug or alcohol violations, an inmate may request and the
5 department shall provide independent confirmation testing of positive
6 results of:
7 (a) Urinalysis urinalysis testing; or .
8 (b) Any screening test, field test, presumptive test, or spot test
9 of an item suspected of being or containing a contraband drug.
10 (2) If the confirmation test remains positive, the inmate may be
11 required to pay the cost of the confirmation test.
12 Sec. 2. Original section 83-4,114.02, Reissue Revised Statutes of
13 Nebraska, is repealed.
